    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know people say things will get better but it just feels like a lie. sometimes i think if i could just find a way to be with him again, i wouldn't have to feel this emptiness anymore. it almost feels more natural to want to go to where he is than to stay here in this silence. do you think i'm just being selfish for feeling like i don't belong here anymore?",
